<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <title>Apple Store - FAQ</title>
  <style>
    .accordion-item {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include ('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
  <div class="container">
    <br>
    <div class="text-center"><h2>Frequently Asked Questions By Customers</h2></div>
    <br>

    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
      
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne">
          Question 1: What is your return policy?
        </button>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Answer: Our return policy allows returns within 30 days of purchase. Please ensure the product is in its original condition.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo">
          Question 2: Can I trade in my old phones for money
        </button>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Answer: Sorry! We do not accept trade ins
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree">
          Question 3: What is the size of an IPhone 15?
        </button>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Answer: Height:	147.6 mm (5.81 in)
                    Width:	71.6 mm (2.82 in)
                    Depth:	7.8 mm (0.31 in)
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour">
          Question 4: How long does delivery usually take?
        </button>
        <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Answer: It really depends on the stock but usually we will have your products delivered to you in less than 3 working days.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive">
          Question 5: Do you guys have any discount codes?
        </button>
        <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Answer: It is on the home page good luck trying to find it!
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSix">
          Question 6: Payment Methods.
        </button>
        <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse">
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Answer: Some payments may be ineligible. If you are using an ineligible payment type, you will have to change the payment method
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
